
  maidodomo ( a mailing list program for postfix )


1. Summary
very simple ML software

2. Setup
create directory "/usr/local/maido"
change mode "777 /usr/local/maido"

copy maido* script to "/usr/local/maido"
change mode "755 maido*"

3. Functions
- create a mailing list
- send mail to mailing list members
- numbering mailing list count

